reviews.text: We enjoyed our first meal so much we came here twice in 3 days. All the dishes were excellent and you won’t be disappointed if you eat here. It’s not the cheapest place to go but it’s worth it. I thought the smoked roast goose was amazing, and so were the roast meats in general, stir fried wing beans with black sauce and the deep fried fish. The tofu fa dessert was also superb, cooked fresh and silky smooth. Because it’s cooked fresh, there’s a bit of a wait but honestly it’s worth it.

Fast efficient service.  Dim sum is not bad.  Dont quite like the taste of puer tea here.  Signature rice roll shrimp spring roll is yummy with the little tempura crisp within that provided a pleasant surprise to the texture.

Not the cleanest dishes. Even the teapots still had food stains on them. Average service attitude and there was more than enough staff. Good food. Tables are too close for comfort. Loud and busy. At least they won’t kick you out for sitting too long. Rare to have ginger pork knuckle on any dim sum menu. Nice twist with the fried tofu wrap with side of puff pastry lobster bisque. Lotus leaf wrapped glutinous rice looks like a slice of cake
The signature fried prawn roll in cheung fan is a real winner. Worth it just for that.. Other dishes are done well and with a great polish.
Nice presentation. The food tasted okay. It seemed a bit pricey for the small portion.

reviews.text:
Nice mall; cool place to be.  Lots of dining options, aside from the usual shopping attractions of the multi-level center.

The series of escalators to the upper floors provide an airy space in the middle of the building.  There is an express escalator straight to the lobby of the offices and hotel, bypassing most of the shopping floors.
Langham Place is awesome shopping place. Wonderful design and place. Outstanding shopping mall. I like it. I am satisfied this Google map.
Very beautiful place i like this place. I will suggest everyone to go there and have fun.  It will be a memorably place
Langham place is the best ever place i have ever visited. People there are very humble with each other and with all the visitors. Amazing place.
Langham Mall is Beautiful shopping mall. Its available all grosery on it. Wonderful shopping mall around the world. I love this place.

reviews.text: 今晚約咗D中學女同學出嚟晚飯飯聚, 侍應服務算 ok 可以, 佢哋嘅中菜小炒幾好食 (用滙豐銀行付款嘅餐牌叫小菜), 首推煲仔上鮑魚炆豬手、 銀雪魚黑松露汁意大利飯 & 豆豉帶子蒸豆腐, 雖然清淡但極美味可口, 不過我哋叫嘅三個甜品全部唔掂唔好食 fail (桶仔豆腐花完全冇豆味又唔夠細滑, 個布甸甜到好厲害 & 個蛋散好睇唔好食, 因為個蛋散居然會係淋嘅唔脆口), 六個女仔叫咗六個小菜, 用滙豐銀行信用卡找數有七五折, 每人消費HK$200 好抵食
高級点心，物有所值。繁忙時間會等很久。
這間酒樓格局高雅，招呼也算周到，食物也可口
